---
title: Beef Rice Noodle Bowls with Carrots, Cucumber, and Peanut Sauce
description: We love trying new ingredients and experimenting with flavors, taking things beyond the ordinary from time to time. This veggie-packed beef noodle bowl is a great way to get everyone at your table to do the same. It features the delightful bounce of rice vermicelli, as well as the incredible aromatics of beef marinated in Thai-style seasonings.
